0.1.name: wordpress/oembed-tweet
0.1.description:
Insert tweeet only input tweet's permalink. You can edit visual design in your theme directory.

This plugin implemented simple template system.

You can edit HTML and Stylesheet in your theme directory. Copy The following files to your theme directory then edit it!

  • oembed_tweet.tpl
  • oembed_tweet.css
